Rules.InvariantScript:
If(
    GLAccountSearch.ResetSearch,
    Defaults('SAP List of Values')
)

Search(//Filter possible list of values according to mapped domain and language field
Sort(
    Filter(
        'SAP List of Values',
        Status = 'Status (SAP List of Values)'.Active,
        Domain = 'Domain (SAP List of Values)'.'Chart Of Account',
        Language = varISOUserLanguageCode
    ),
    'Display Value'
),cmbGLAccountSearchChartOfAccounts.SearchText,"mpa_value","mpa_valuecode")

With(
    {defaultHeight: 64},
    Switch(
        true,
        Self.Width <= 500,
        3 * defaultHeight + 2 * Self.LayoutGap,
        Self.Width <= 750,
        2 * defaultHeight + Self.LayoutGap,
        defaultHeight
    )
)

If(
    Or(
        IsEmpty(colGLAccountSearchResults),
        varIsProcessing
    ),
    DisplayMode.Disabled,
    DisplayMode.Edit
)

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
//Display GL account search result items for collection cached
With(
    {
        searchResults: If(
            IsBlank(txtGLAccountSearchResultsFilter.Text),//Show all results if no filtered text entered
            First(colGLAccountSearchResults).List,
            Search(//Otherwise, search on the results further using entered filtered text
                First(colGLAccountSearchResults).List,
                txtGLAccountSearchResultsFilter.Text,
                "Account",
                "Chart",
                "Description"
            )
        )
    },
    SortByColumns(
        searchResults,
        Switch(
            varGLAccountSearchAllSortByColumn,//determine which field to sort by based upon the tabel header column value selected and stored in variable
            btnGLAccountSearchResultsTabelHeaderAccount.Text,
            "Account",
            btnGLAccountSearchResultsTabelHeaderDescription.Text,
            "Description",
            btnGLAccountSearchResultsTabelHeaderChartOfAccounts.Text,
            "Chart"
        ),
        varGLAccountSearchAllSortOrder//sort ascending or descending based upon value stored in variable
    )
)

Rule.InvariantScript: lblGLAccountsNumberOfFoundRecords.Height + conGLAccountSearchResults.LayoutMinHeight + conGLAccountSearchAllFields.Height + conGLAccountSearchButtons.Height + Self.PaddingTop + Self.PaddingBottom + Self.LayoutGap * 2 + 10

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(280, Self.Width - 60), Min(280, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
//Display recent search result items for collection sorting according to table header buttons selected
With(
    {
        recentItems: If(
            IsBlank(txtGLAccountRecentlySearchedCommandBarFilter.Text),//Show all results if no filter text entered
            Filter(
                'SAP Search Histories',
                'SAP Search Histories (Views)'.'My Recent SAP Search History',//Entity view that has filter logic to return user's search history records
                'Object Type' = 'Object Type (SAP Search Histories)'.'GL Account'//Filter on object type vendor
            ),
            Search(//Otherwise, search results based upon filtered text entered
                Filter(
                    'SAP Search Histories',
                    'SAP Search Histories (Views)'.'My Recent SAP Search History',//Entity view that has filter logic to return user's search history records
                    'Object Type' = 'Object Type (SAP Search Histories)'.'GL Account'//Filter on object type vendor
                ),
                txtGLAccountRecentlySearchedCommandBarFilter.Text,
                "mpa_name",
                "mpa_objectid"
            )
        )
    },
    SortByColumns(
        recentItems,
        Switch(
            varRecentlySearchedSortByColumn,//determine which field to sort by based upon the tabel header column value selected and stored in variable
            btnGLAccountRecentlySearchedResultsHeaderAccount.Text,
            "mpa_objectid",
            btnGLAccountRecentlySearchedResultsHeaderDescription.Text,
            "mpa_name",
            btnGLAccountRecentlySearchedResultsHeaderChartOfAccounts.Text,
            "mpa_attribute1",
            btnGLAccountRecentlySearchedResultsHeaderLastSearched.Text,
            "mpa_lastsearchedon"
        ),
        varRecentlySearchedSortOrder//sort ascending or descending based upon value stored in variable
    )
)

!IsEmpty(
    Filter(
        'SAP Search Histories',
        'SAP Search Histories (Views)'.'My Recent SAP Search History',//Entity view that has filter logic to return user's search history records
        'Object Type' = 'Object Type (SAP Search Histories)'.'GL Account'//Filter on object type vendor
    )
)
